    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171310/extras/c1cd0665ed4539aea6e91d2836c30748.avif?t=1731071176\" width=600 height=135 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这里，你可以举起任何能够互动的物品，无论是防御塔、路障还是敌人都没有问题，每个关卡都不止一种通关方式，你需要找到最适合你的游戏玩法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171310/extras/65797e8b593571376040acc2e610a44e.poster.avif?t=1731071176\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171310/extras/65797e8b593571376040acc2e610a44e.webm?t=1731071176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171310/extras/65797e8b593571376040acc2e610a44e.mp4?t=1731071176\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171310/extras/de180d9f47ab60598a705184df136945.avif?t=1731071176\" width=600 height=135 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《太阳石大战：序章》将免费提供11个关卡供玩家们挑战，横跨3片不同的区域，草原、雷霆平原以及火山，每个关卡都有独特的怪物、路障和机制玩法，你会享受在这款超有特色的塔防游戏中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171310/extras/cffdb184647adc635859b4b931ef9f65.poster.avif?t=1731071176\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171310/extras/cffdb184647adc635859b4b931ef9f65.webm?t=1731071176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171310/extras/cffdb184647adc635859b4b931ef9f65.mp4?t=1731071176\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171310/extras/2f8456efc75b0fc05c7ce23bf2be951b.avif?t=1731071176\" width=600 height=135 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个区域的怪物都有自己的特性，像是快如闪电的敌人，或者是能用舌头把你吸走的怪物等等，当然你也得有应对措施，比如举起后可以吸取雷电之力的雷霆石，或者抓取后会蜷缩成球状并攻击队友的敌人，总有让你感到惊喜的游戏内容！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171310/extras/f2e8920781f4d774fb015cf9b1f2d9aa.poster.avif?t=1731071176\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171310/extras/f2e8920781f4d774fb015cf9b1f2d9aa.webm?t=1731071176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171310/extras/f2e8920781f4d774fb015cf9b1f2d9aa.mp4?t=1731071176\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
